  <Placemark>
      <name>TORRE DEL FERRO</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Istanza di permesso di ricerca in terraferma</h3><h2>TORRE DEL FERRO</h2><br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Data&nbsp;di&nbsp;presentazione&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">22/02/2012</td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Superficie</th><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">118 km<sup>2</sup></td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Fogli IGM</th><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">221-222-229-230&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>Richiedenti</th><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;">APENNINE&nbsp;ENERGY&nbsp;(100%&nbsp;r.u.)<br></td></tr></tr></table><br>UBICAZIONE<br><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" valign=top>Calabria (118,00&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup>)<br>Cosenza (118,00&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup>)<br><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" width=350 align=left valign=top>Comuni:<br>Cassano allo Ionio, Corigliano Calabro, Terranova di Sibari, San Giorgio Albanese, Rossano.</td></td></tr></table><br>COORDINATE GEOGRAFICHE DEI VERTICI<table style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid grey;"><tr><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Vertice</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Longitudine</th><th style="padding: 4px; background-color:#E4E4E4; color:grey; border: 1px solid grey;">Latitudine</th></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>a</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordm; 00&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>39&ordm; 45&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>b</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Intersezione tra il parallelo 39&ordm;45&apos; e la linea di costa a bassa marea&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>c</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Intersezione tra la linea di costa a bassa marea ed il parallelo 39&ordm;38&apos;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>d</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordm; 01&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>39&ordm; 38&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>e</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordm; 01&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>39&ordm; 39&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>f</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3&ordm; 57&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>39&ordm; 39&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>g</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>3&ordm; 57&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>39&ordm; 43&apos;</td></tr><tr><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>h</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>4&ordm; 00&apos;</td><td style="padding: 2px 4px 2px 4px; border: 1px solid grey;" align=center>39&ordm; 43&apos;</td></tr></table><br>Le informazioni sulla fase e sull&apos;iter del procedimento amministrativo sono in corso di aggiornamento.<br><br>]]></description>
